{"tid":1803063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中原地產周末10大屋苑錄得5宗成交按周升66.7%","createTime":"2019-12-30T02:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T03:48:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75b92095db965b22ce80a09e6a185fe076c0287c","tid":1803063,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:33:39.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 中原地產10大屋苑本周末錄得5宗成交,雖較上周末3宗升66.7%,但仍屬低水平,其中亦有5個屋苑錄得零成交,已連續8周錄得個位數交投量。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示,聖誕假期過後,買賣雙方陸續回復正常睇樓活動,一手貨尾銷情不錯,料市況向好發展。惟近日市場焦點集中於新界西新盤,加上新一期綠置居開始接受申請,扣起市場上大批二手購買力,料二手交投會逐步回復正常水平。 (BC)"},{"pid":"6e187ab15fb43350c3b8da6ecce6fbbefcd3c1f0","tid":1803063,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"升好多呀，樓市gogogo"},{"pid":"633adf023054a8103ef3fe23b714daf07e52caa4","tid":1803063,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSU2qmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSU2qmP.jpg&h=0ee870ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skMss7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2skMss7.jpg&h=077c238a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門<br />\n<br />\n1230 愛丁堡廣場 痛心疾首追悼會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802577</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥) (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最新日程表出咗啦 除夕元旦都有行動呀<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/1798785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1798785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"